    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's just something people say to feel better. it's not actually true. if you look at the physics of it, there is no \"reason.\" there's just cause and effect. there's no grand design or some invisible hand making sure things work out. it just feels like i'm watching a movie that's already been decided, and the ending is just... nothing. how can you say there's a reason when there literally isn't one?",
